modName: Closed-Face Elven Helmet and Masked Hooded Thalmor Robes
descriptionHtml:
I always thought the Elven armor and Thalmor robes would look much more intimidating if they concealed your face. So I went and did just that. If I get enough requests for it, I\'ll make seperate versions for both the Helmet and the Robes.

Also I highly recommend using Shodan44\'s black and gold elven armor with this as it yields amazing results with this new helmet. [url=http://skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=6524]You can get it here.[/url]
author: JayMercer
